<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Claude Code Newsletter</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    /* Wrapper */
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 24px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
      padding: 36px 40px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .header-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(91, 106, 240, 0.3);
      color: #a0aaff;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    /* Body */
    .body {
      padding: 36px 40px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .body h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .body h2 {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #2d2d44;
      margin-top: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .body h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .body p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #555;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .body a {
      color: #5b6af0;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .body a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .body ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin: 8px 0 16px;
    }
    .body li {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .body hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #ececec;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    .body strong {
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #ececec;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #5b6af0;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Mobile */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
      .wrapper { margin: 0; border-radius: 0; }
      .header, .body, .footer { padding: 24px 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-badge">Weekly</div>
      <h1>Claude Code Newsletter</h1>
      <p>매주 일요일 · 전세계 Claude Code 활용 사례 모음</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="body">
      {{ content | safe }}
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        이 뉴스레터는 자동으로 생성됩니다.<br>
        <a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}">구독 해지</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Claude Code Newsletter
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
